Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:11.11,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:38.18,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first round of the second stage \Nof the Royal Knights Selection Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:43.18,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Sol's attack left Mimosa unable to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:47.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta was forced to face off with Magna, \Nwho came to attack their crystal on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:48.40,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:51.28,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:54.45,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I'm not gonna be able \Nto take both of them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:58.82,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The one who saved Asta was a \Nmysterious mage named Xerx.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:01.54,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the cherry blossom guy,\Nyou little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.41,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of this in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:06.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And that instant's all I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:13.21,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,With the help of Mimosa's plant spell that \Nlets her control the enemy's movements,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:17.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the rest of B Team \Nwere able to claim victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:24.15,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the destined battle between the\Nbrothers Finral and Langris is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:57.03,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Special Little Brother\N vs.\N Failed Big Brother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.84,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:04.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you, Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:08.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect! You look awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:10.18,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Could you do mine, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.25,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You already lost, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:15.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It looks fine. You look like \Nthe failure that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.80,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Who're you calling a failure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.73,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Try to stay calm, Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.20,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Like a loser should.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.30,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.54,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Let's do this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you guys—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.80,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, that guy is a very \Nskilled flame magic caster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.65,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,The lightning guy is also \None to look out for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:41.42,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.22,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Luck is trying to cheer him up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:47.54,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La, la. Gimme more noms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.16,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,My, aren't you a hungry little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:54.12,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie... Marie... Always Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.09,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.03,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.42,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess bulls will be bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:04.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you guys, stop! \NThis is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:13.56,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.06,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this next match
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.36,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,will be complicated for you, \Ngiven who you're up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:20.17,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Y-Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:24.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I've never beaten \Nmy little brother in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.66,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.62,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought alongside you, so I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.41,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You changed after meeting Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.08,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:38.67,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to face something hidden deep\N within my heart that I'd been ignoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:42.02,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to lose so easily now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:45.18,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Now get out there and show everyone \Nhow cool you are. Just like your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.68,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:52.62,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose like Magna, and come fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:56.57,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Don't lose like— \NThe hell did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:59.72,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm rooting for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:06.99,top,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this. You've got this. You've got this. \NYou've got this. You've got this. You've got this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:05.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not embarrass \Nthe rest of the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:06.99,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.99,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Charmy... Even Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:14.75,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you guys. I'm so happy \NI joined the Black Bu—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:18.54,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Please, more noms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:21.59,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Marie as soon as possible, \Nso win this in one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:24.19,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But I have seniority...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:27.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Captain Yami's cheering \Nyou on from the base, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:30.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He seemed a bit antsy this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He said his stomach was acting up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:37.27,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he just wants to see you \Nwork hard even without his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:43.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys must be going beyond their \Nlimits and kicking ass right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kicking ass, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.16,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This one's gonna be a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And damn it, kid! I told you to \Nrestock the damn toilet paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:58.42,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. As if you could \Nactually defeat me, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.65,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris, I managed to change \Nafter meeting my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.00,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be the ones who win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:08.01,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Don't blame me for \Nwhatever happens, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Would you let me handle him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.54,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.33,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,A battle between brothers, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:19.00,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to fight my \Nbrother for real one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.98,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your passionate request!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.18,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:25.80,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to burn the image \Nof me gallantly riding
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.18,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,my Shooting Star into everyone's eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:30.99,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,You will not lay a single \Nfinger on our crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.29,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Finral, I know you can win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.43,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:46.29,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,E Team: Leopold, Hamon, and Finral \Nversus G Team: Langris, Fragil, and Sekke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.05,sign_10657_102_Roland,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Fragil
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.05,sign_9718_95_Langris,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Langris
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.05,sign_10657_103_Nix,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sekke
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.05,sign_10224_105_D_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}G Team
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.05,sign_9718_98_Leopold,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Leopold
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.05,sign_9718_99_Finral,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Finral
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.05,sign_9718_100_Hamon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hamon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.05,sign_10224_103_C_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}E Team
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:48.47,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Round two of stage two, begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:51.77,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You two concentrate on \Ndestroying the enemy crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.84,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.31,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find out where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.45,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Glass Magic: Verre Détection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:08.32,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I can see every inch of this battle stage \Nas the light reflects off the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:14.29,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,It will take a little while, but I will \Ndefinitely be able to find the enemy's crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:24.07,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to take me all the way \Nto the enemy base again, Mr. Bah-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.81,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me! Also, I'm Sekke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.90,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Sekke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.40,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You can even call me Sek, bah-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.22,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Mr. Bah-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.82,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha. No, really, it's Sekke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.56,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Sekke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.81,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You brought shame upon the House of Vaude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:44.35,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can defeat me, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.70,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You see, you aren't my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:53.18,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So the only one that I love \Nis my dear little Langris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.33,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, it's a bit cruel to be so blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.79,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What is that pathetically weak spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.76,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Learn from Langris's attack spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.97,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.42,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I see my dear little Langris is better \Nthan you at both academics and sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:17.30,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're so amazing, my dear little Langris.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.73,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,As I should expect from my own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.57,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Finral?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.19,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You disgrace the Vaude name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:32.07,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic. He's older than me, but there's \Nnot one thing he can do better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.34,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What? A fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.32,flashbacktop,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:40.60,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(968,998)}Finnes Calmreich
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:39.90,flashbacktop,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,This is Lady Finnes, the fiancée of \Nthe next head of the House of Vaude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.63,flashback,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:47.69,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Her chronic illness keeps \Nher from going out often,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:50.94,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,but the king is her great uncle, \Nso she comes from a prestigious family
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:53.42,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,and has splendid magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.61,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, in the future, \Nthis woman and I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:09:00.93,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh. What a dull-looking woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:05.10,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,My dear little Langris, \Nmake sure you get along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.19,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to be your bride someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.90,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:15.21,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... When I become \Nthe lord of this house,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:20.08,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to bring us fame \Nlike they've never seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.89,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... I'm so bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:31.34,flashback,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry that you got stuck with a \Nfiancée who's sickly and older than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:36.70,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all! \NYou're b-b-beautiful, Miss Finnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:42.18,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... I'm not the one who'll become \Nthe next head of the House of Vaude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.55,flashback,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:46.05,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother is better \Nat everything than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.15,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,so he'll be able to make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.66,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,His magic is amazing, \Nand he's a very decisive person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.28,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:59.62,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. There's not a single \Nthing he can beat me i—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.12,flashback,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.12,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:05.13,flashback,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,I've only met you a few times, but I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:08.11,flashback,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:11.88,flashback,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,To me, you're a much more \Nwonderful mage, Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:17.80,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, stop! D-Don't tease me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.49,flashback,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I wasn't teasing you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.11,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are, you dull woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:26.60,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You have the nerve to call me \Ninferior to my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:28.42,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.61,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,That loser left the family because \Nhe couldn't handle the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:35.98,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,He's not better than me at anything!\NNot a single thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.36,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:44.98,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes. As we planned, \Nwe'll leave him to you, Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:50.41,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Just as a reminder...\NDon't blame me if you lose any limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.29,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end this in a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:57.42,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:03.80,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I tested this out earlier with another \Nspatial magic user, Cob, and found out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.39,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,that when spatial magics collide,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:09.88,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,the mana currents collide \Nand cancel each other out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:13.02,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris, we're the ones who are going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:28.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You can cancel out spatial \Nmagic with spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.48,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:34.02,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's like a completely different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.52,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up, ya jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:39.06,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's waiting. Hurry up and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.78,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I get to have more yummy noms, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.26,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha, ha-bah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.93,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, Finral! That was effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.27,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hamon, where's the enemy team's crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:56.86,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.82,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,It's deep within that tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm counting on you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.66,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't good, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:09.16,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are, Brother? \NI'll remind you of your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.75,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.88,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,You came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.26,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:28.76,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,Snow Magic: Phantom Snow Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:33.37,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,This spell forces your senses to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.02,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot attack me effectively any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:44.25,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not tired at all... This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:49.28,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Especially compared to my older sister's \Ntraining, which could leave you dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:52.54,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you still have much to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.79,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're so valiant, Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.72,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I can still eat plenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.42,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.76,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,You should give up and fall asleep, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:08.76,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:13.14,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,I swore upon the symbol on my forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:16.60,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,that I would surpass my brother someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:19.56,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,And that means I can't lose in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.27,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.08,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Mana Skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:28.28,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Spiral Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.56,italics,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,His senses are sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:37.04,italics,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,He enveloped himself in mana \Nand canceled my spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:40.54,italics,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,More! I need to concentrate more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:45.05,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,I won't last much longer, Langris.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.22,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:59.04,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,A spatial magic battle! \NYou don't see that every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.86,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that is Finnes's fiancé, Langris.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.83,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:06.53,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,He's still no match for me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:09.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:12.83,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time before \Ntheir crystal is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:17.37,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd become \Nmy natural enemy, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:21.46,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan on defending \Nuntil our crystal breaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.38,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure that'll be so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.38,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It might not be. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:30.26,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use a new spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:36.52,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! What in the world is that slow spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:40.37,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Like you could hit my badass self right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:44.11,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,What? Homing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:50.75,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,That's no match for my invincible \NSekke Magnum Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-He disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.42,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty pathetic, even for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:04.34,main,Fnral,0000,0000,0000,,I trained so hard, but I never \Ncould learn a single attack spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:07.34,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an attack spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:11.94,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic: Fallen Angel's Wingbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It follows the enemy, \Nand once it makes contact,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.75,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,it transports them to another location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:19.81,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's the applied version of \Nthe spell I usually use.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:25.93,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This way, he can get rid of \Nenemies without hurting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:29.03,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,He must be a kind soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:32.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're so awesome, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.62,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,B-But where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It just went back in. Can I kill you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.84,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha... I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:58.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris, it's only a matter of time \Nbefore your crystal is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hurt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.65,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on continuing, I'll have \Nto use this spell to make you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.63,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who{\i0} are you worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:17.38,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You constantly get on my nerves, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:20.95,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought that our special \Nreserve spells would be similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:33.22,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make me use my grimoire's magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:45.65,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a single thing \Nyou can beat me at, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:51.90,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This ominous feeling... \NI've felt this somewhere before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:54.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.24,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:01.75,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't feel very pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.50,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,As I figured...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.50,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.25,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:16.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This immense magical power... \NI already know I don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:18.01,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.02,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,This nauseating magic is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:25.02,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If that attack hits him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.81,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:35.69,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No. He's Langris.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He's my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.20,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You may not like it, but we're similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.45,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Our mothers are different, but in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.95,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I never did anything that made \Nme seem like a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:52.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I left our family and tried \Nto forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:02.49,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But I just couldn't. \NLangris, no matter what you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:04.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You're my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:14.23,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris, stop it! If you keep this up, \NI have a feeling you won't be you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:18.09,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,What could you possibly \Nknow about me, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.27,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You left everything behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:23.49,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You're a coward who can't even hurt people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:27.25,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare try to act \Nlike my big brother now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.75,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.40,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,G-G Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:10.50,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that? \NThere's nothing you can beat me at!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:16.94,flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master Finral is so friendly and kind, \Nisn't he? He has a lot of friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:23.56,flashback,Lady 2,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master Langris is... Well, it's obvious\N that he looks down on people, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:29.43,flashback,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,To me, you're a much more \Nwonderful mage, Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:34.69,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Even I want someone that kind to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.19,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:41.34,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Working too hard all the time \Nhurts after a while, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:43.49,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Come goof off with your \Nbig brother once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.87,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,There's a festival going on nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:49.41,flashbackitalics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he nice to me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.54,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.44,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Learn from Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.67,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,My dear little Langris is so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:59.53,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I'm better than you are. That's why \NMother and Father are kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:06.05,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I have to beat him at everything! \NOtherwise, I'll... I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:12.41,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the match is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.56,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.36,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.04,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.42,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,These wounds are awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.71,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:42.13,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Just try and do something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:45.97,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the match. We'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.10,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:49.05,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to Finral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.36,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is too awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.85,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,You actually pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.35,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:57.98,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:03.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The match was already over!
