Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:37.32,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:42.04,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Hairstyle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:40.03,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:46.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That new spell is awesome! \NFallen Angel's Weightlifting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:48.89,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's Fallen Angel's Wingbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:51.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I know when I need to get tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:53.69,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's the result of trying different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:59.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So is your new hairstyle also \Nfrom trying different things?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:00.93,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:02.15,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you tried out a regent pompadour.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.83,0:23:07.64,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,As well as Captain Yami's hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:09.90,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,And soft serve hair, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:10.94,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's poo—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:12.99,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This looks pretty strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.79,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,If you do Marie's hairstyle, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:18.67,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-I like this hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.67,0:23:21.71,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I think this one is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:23.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's just a better option, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:25.66,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,How about something a bit more mature?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:28.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is the hairstyle for when \Nyou go beyond your limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:30.25,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.25,0:23:34.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see this \Nhairstyle on you, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:38.17,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to me in this series, \Nmy hair should be the least of your worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:41.98,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Praise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:44.73,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Your daring and resolute king presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:51.65,main,king,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 81:\N"The Life of a Certain Man."
